:: RP-05 {"position":"454,195","size":"100,100"}
<<set $passage to "RP-05">><<set $nextpassage to "RP-06">>
<main><<audio ":all" stop>><<audio "RP_05" play>>


Sometimes when my bus gets in early, I like to come here for a few moments and look up at the Monument and imagine the City on fire.

Two thirds of it, blazing for three days.

Not that I want that to happen. Of course not. I love London. I never felt like I belonged at home. It’s not like I belong here either. It’s just that nobody belongs here so we all belong.

